{"tid":1439001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【內部勢力】支那有邊幾個城市有獨立思想？","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:25:25.000Z","uid":37528,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8974d66b2feadf0ad5134bdd195ff31e2b76d562","tid":1439001,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"除左上海，支那仲有咩城市有獨立既傾向？<br />\n之前有張圖係講全支那既經濟，主要靠幾個城市撐起，廣東就好似係賺得最多既地方<br />\n<br />\n我地面對除左係港共政權，仲有呢個仆街共產黨。我地唔係想解放中國，不過只係想黎個真正圍趙救魏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新疆，西藏唔講因為已經被打壓得好厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c250709a62afd7a9a5d74702e7ab54f3500c28","tid":1439001,"uid":265443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:22:49.000Z","msg":"上海"},{"pid":"7066d0a7fdbe41ac8a35e3cf39898e3a8714b4f3","tid":1439001,"uid":47669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"廣州？廈門？"},{"pid":"cf9c6c264ae738365e8a8b63df47670d42986ed1","tid":1439001,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"如果你講離心力同獨立傾向<br />\n基本上只有上海同廣州係濃少少<br />\n(但我覺得唔會濃得去邊)<br />\n<br />\n上海<br />\n背景同我地有少少像<br />\n外國殖民年代 帶比佢地好多野<br />\n所以佢地無法好像一般中國人全盤否定<br />\n晚清西方入侵<br />\n<br />\n本土吳語都受嚴重打擊<br />\n被外省人換血 問題都嚴重"},{"pid":"e32fcf49f71a5d5b80680ab700e19c169cf78b5e","tid":1439001,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7066d0a7fdbe41ac8a35e3cf39898e3a8714b4f3","tid":1439001,"uid":47669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"廣州？廈門？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:31:11.000Z","msg":"唔明點解廣州咁多人當香港係敵人，明明係被支那蝦得最勁果批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廈門好似俾支那同化曬"},{"pid":"273d65c7db05bbecf7952743d3e467e56